    <briefdescription>
<para>STM32 CAN implementation. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Design:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Supports both bxCAN and FDCAN via a variant tag + union of handles.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>SendMessage/ReceiveMessage use blocking HAL calls.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Acceptance filter wraps HAL filter configuration.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Receive callback stored for ISR forwarding. </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
